## D. Status Kesiapan Fitur (Sudah Berfungsi vs Belum)

| Fitur | Status | Penjelasan |
|---|---|---|
| ✅ Clipboard Watcher | **Berfungsi** | Polling 250ms, deteksi perubahan |
| ✅ Cleaning Pipeline | **Berfungsi** | Middleware pattern, sudah terintegrasi plugin hooks |
| ✅ Content Detection | **Berfungsi** | 12+ tipe konten terdeteksi |
| ✅ Security Scanner | **Berfungsi** | 10 pola PII, masking full/partial |
| ✅ Context Guard | **Berfungsi** | Blokir paste ke app terlarang |
| ✅ Auto-Clear | **Berfungsi** | Timer-based clipboard clear |
| ✅ SQLite Database | **Berfungsi** | 6+ tabel, FTS5 search, WAL mode |
| ✅ History CRUD | **Berfungsi** | List, pin, delete, bulk actions |
| ✅ Snippets CRUD | **Berfungsi** | Create, read, update, delete |
| ✅ Templates | **Berfungsi** | Variable parsing & filling |
| ✅ Settings Store | **Berfungsi** | JSON config, disk persistence |
| ✅ System Tray | **Berfungsi** | Context menu, preset toggle |
| ✅ Hotkey Manager | **Berfungsi** | globalShortcut registration |
| ✅ IPC Handlers | **Berfungsi** | 25+ channels, modular per domain |
| ✅ Dashboard | **Berfungsi** | Statistik, top types, recent clips |
| ✅ Cross-Device Sync | **Berfungsi** | WebSocket, E2E encrypted, relay protocol |
| ✅ Extension Server | **Berfungsi** | Named pipe untuk browser extension |
| ✅ Floating Toast | **Berfungsi** | Context-aware action buttons |
| ⚠️ AI Rewriter | **Parsial** | Hanya bekerja jika user punya API key OpenAI. Tanpa key → return teks asli tanpa perubahan |
| ⚠️ Plugin System | **Parsial** | API & hooks terdefinisi, tapi belum ada plugin yang bisa diinstall/diaktifkan dari UI |
| ⚠️ Multi-Clipboard | **Parsial** | Backend logic ada, tapi tidak ada UI untuk kontrol on/off atau melihat buffer |
| ⚠️ Paste Queue | **Parsial** | Backend logic ada, tapi tidak ada UI untuk kontrol atau melihat antrian |
| ⚠️ Format Converter | **Parsial** | JSON↔YAML↔TOML ada, tapi tidak ada UI tombol "Convert to..." |
| ❌ OCR Engine | **Stub** | Fungsi [recognizeText()](file:///c:/Users/USER/Downloads/smartpastehub/src/ocr/ocr-engine.ts#18-26) hanya return objek kosong `{ text: '', confidence: 0 }` |
| ❌ Screen Capture | **Stub** | File [screen-capture.ts](file:///c:/Users/USER/Downloads/smartpastehub/src/ocr/screen-capture.ts) ada tapi belum diimplementasi |
| ❌ QR Bridge Pairing | **Stub** | HTML entry point ada, tapi tidak ada kode untuk generate/scan QR |
| ❌ Auto Updater | **Placeholder** | Kode dikomentari, hanya log "scaffold initialized" |

---

## E. Apakah Semua Fitur Butuh Frontend?

| Fitur | Butuh Frontend? | Alasan |
|---|---|---|
| Clipboard Watcher | **Tidak** | Sepenuhnya background, user tidak perlu melihat apapun |
| Cleaning Pipeline | **Tidak** | Otomatis via hotkey, tanpa UI |
| Content Detection | **Tidak** | Otomatis di backend |
| Security Scanner | **Minimal** | Hanya butuh toast/notifikasi, bukan halaman penuh |
| Auto-Clear | **Tidak** | Timer di backend, hanya perlu toast konfirmasi |
| Context Guard | **Minimal** | Hanya butuh toast peringatan |
| Hotkey | **Tidak** | Backend intercept, tanpa UI |
| Extension Server | **Tidak** | Backend-only, berkomunikasi langsung via named pipe |
| History | **Ya** | User perlu menelusuri, mencari, dan mengelola riwayat |
| Snippets | **Ya** | User perlu membuat, mengedit, dan mengatur snippet |
| Templates | **Ya** | User perlu mengisi variabel, membuat template baru |
| Settings | **Ya** | User perlu mengkonfigurasi preferensi |
| Dashboard | **Ya** | User perlu melihat statistik penggunaan |
| AI Rewriter | **Opsional** | Bisa via floating toast action, tidak perlu halaman khusus |
| OCR | **Ya** (jika diimplementasi) | User perlu crop area layar dan melihat hasil |
| Sync | **Ya** | User perlu pairing device, melihat status koneksi |
| Multi-Clipboard | **Ya** | User perlu melihat buffer dan mengontrol mode |
| Paste Queue | **Ya** | User perlu melihat dan mengatur urutan antrian |
| Plugin Management | **Ya** | User perlu install, toggle, dan konfigurasi plugin |
| Format Converter | **Opsional** | Bisa otomatis di pipeline, tapi tombol manual akan berguna |

### Ringkasan
- **7 fitur** berjalan sepenuhnya di background tanpa UI
- **6 fitur** membutuhkan halaman/UI penuh
- **4 fitur** bisa opsional (cukup toast/action bar)
- **4 fitur** masih stub/belum berfungsi dan butuh implementasi + UI
